title: League of Legends not launching
body:
When i open my league of legends , the client doesnt open nothing happens.

My pc:
4 gb ram
Pentium(R) Dual-Core CPU E5300 2.60GHz 
64 bit
Graphics:
Nvidia Geforce 9600 GT 
512mb
Total available graphics memory:
2303 mb 
Can anyone fix this problem please
btw
Windows 7

replies.body: Most likely this is happening from your OS not having the right permissions setup. You should be able to get the client to launch correctly by following the steps in our [**permissions guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions).
